General.Name: Leslies Inc
General.Description: Leslie's, Inc. operates as a direct-to-consumer pool and spa care brand in the United States. The company markets and sells pool and spa supplies and related products and services. It also offers various pool and spa maintenance items, such as chemicals, equipment and parts, and cleaning accessories, as well as safety, recreational, and fitness related products. In addition, the company provides installation and repair services for pool and spa equipment. It also sells its products through e-commerce websites and third-party marketplaces. The company offers complimentary and commercial-grade in-store water testing and analysis services. It serves residential, professional, and commercial consumers. The company was founded in 1963 and is headquartered in Phoenix, Arizona.
